title: Wipfratal
text:
Wipfratal is a former municipality in the district <a href="Ilm-Kreis">Ilm-Kreis</a>, in <a href="Thuringia">Thuringia</a>, <a href="Germany">Germany</a>. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the town <a href="Arnstadt">Arnstadt</a>.
Wipratal consisted of the following villages: Branchewinda, Dannheim, Ettischleben, Görbitzhausen, Hausen, Kettmanshausen, Marlishausen, Neuroda, Reinsfeld, Roda, Schmerfeld and Wipfra.
